{"pageProps":{"source":"<div class=\"space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0\"><p>Pour créer un fichier <code>.gitignore</code> rapidement, il existe le service <a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://gitignore.io/\">gitignore.io</a>.</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\"># .bashrc\ngi () {\n    curl -L &quot;https://gitignore.io/api/$@&quot;\n}\n</code></pre></div><p>À chaque fois que je souhaite créer un fichier <code>.gitignore</code>, pour un projet Nodejs par exemple, j&#x27;exécute la commande suivante :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">gi node &gt; .gitignore\n</code></pre></div></div>","isIndex":false,"file":"gitignore.md","fileName":"gitignore","title":"Créer un fichier .gitignore automatiquement","comments":true,"permalink":"creer-un-fichier-.gitignore","aliases":"[.gitignore]","datePublished":"2021-06-27T19:19","dateUpdated":"2021-06-27T19:19","publish":true,"rss":true,"note":"48"},"__N_SSG":true}